### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@caseId = CASE-0001
@accountId = ACC-0001

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### 2. Retrieve Case by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/cases/{{caseId}}

### 3. Retrieve KYC Record by Account ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/kyc

### 4. Retrieve Account Transactions (All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions

### 5. Retrieve Account Transactions (Filtered by since_days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions?since_days=30

### 6. Raise Risk Flag
POST {{baseUrl}}/flags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "{{accountId}}",
  "reason": "Suspicious transaction volume",
  "raised_by": "vscode-rest-client"
}
